{
  "texts": [
    "These advancements are not without limitations.",
    "The effectiveness of LLMs largely depend on the quality and coverage of the available training datasets.",
    "The model predictions in breeding decisions can be biased due to incomplete data, limiting the potential value of the model.",
    "Additionally, the computational resources required for training large models can pose accessibility challenges, particularly in regions with limited technological infrastructure.",
    "However, there are several ways to effectively measure LLMs into plant breeding workflow."
  ]
}